# Sales Forecasting Dashboard

This folder contains the Power BI dashboard developed for the Sales Forecasting & Revenue Analytics project. 
The dashboard provides interactive visualizations to analyze historical sales performance and monitor key business metrics.

## Dashboard Content

The dashboard includes the following visualizations:

• Total Revenue KPI – Displays overall revenue generated from sales data  
• Monthly Sales Trend – Shows revenue trends over time to identify growth patterns  
• Sales by Product Category – Highlights the performance of different product categories  
• Top-Selling Products – Identifies the products generating the highest revenue  
• Regional Sales Analysis – Compares sales performance across different regions  
• Profit Margin Analysis – Evaluates profitability across products and regions  
• Forecasted Sales Trend – Displays predicted sales using time-series forecasting models

## Purpose of the Dashboard

The dashboard helps businesses:

• Monitor revenue performance in real time  
• Identify high-performing products and regions  
• Detect seasonal sales trends  
• Support data-driven decision making  
• Improve sales forecasting and planning

## Tools Used

• Power BI  
• Python (for data preprocessing and forecasting)  
• SQL (for sales data analysis)
